'''白兀鷲'''（[[學名|學名]]：''{{lang|la|Neophron percnopterus}}''），又名'''埃及禿鷲'''，是一種稀少的[[禿鷲|禿鷲]]。它們分佈在[[歐洲|歐洲]]西南部及[[非洲|非洲]]北部至[[南亞|南亞]]。它們的翼底呈黑白色，尾巴呈楔狀。它們有時會用石頭敲破鳥蛋，是少數懂得使用工具的[[鳥類|鳥類]]之一。在[[溫帶|溫帶]][[繁殖|繁殖]]的群落會向南遷徙過冬，而在[[熱帶|熱帶]]的多是[[留鳥|留鳥]]。它們的數量於20世紀有所下降，而在[[島嶼|島嶼]]中的群落則特別[[瀕危|瀕危]]。

== 特徵 ==
[[File:Neophron_percnopterus.JPG|thumb]]
白兀鷲的[[羽毛|羽毛]]是白色的，飛羽黑色。它們的身體有時有些泥色是與其習性有關。喙幼長，上頷端有鈎。鼻孔很長。[[頸部|頸部]]羽毛很長，雙翼很尖，當中以第三主羽最長。尾巴呈楔狀。爪子直而且長，第三及第四趾有小蹼。指名亞種的喙是黑色的，而[[印度|印度]][[亞種|亞種]]''N. p. ginginianus''的則較為淡色或黃色，但這種變化仍需更多證據支持。<ref name=pcr>{{cite book|author=Rasmussen PC & JC Anderton|year=2005| title=Birds of South Asia: The Ripley Guide. Volume 2|page=89| publisher=Smithsonian Institution and Lynx Edicions}}</ref>面部[[皮膚|皮膚]]是黃色的。<ref name=hbk>{{cite book|author=Ali S & SD Ripley|title=Handbook of the birds of India and Pakistan. Volume 1|edition=2|publisher=Oxford University Press|year=1978|pages=310–4}}</ref>雛鳥是黑色或深褐色的，有黑白色的斑。<ref name=hbk/>成年的白兀鷲全長85厘米，翼展1.7米。它們重約2公斤，但''N. p. majorensis''則平均重2.4公斤。<ref name=canary/>

== 分類 ==
[[白兀鷲屬|白兀鷲屬]]只有白兀鷲一個[[物種|物種]]。此屬相信是最古老的[[禿鷲|禿鷲]]分支之一，現存的最近親是[[胡兀鷲|胡兀鷲]]。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Phylogeny of Old and New World Vultures (Aves: Accipitridae and Cathartidae) Inferred from Nucleotide Sequences of the Mitochondrial Cytochrome b Gene|author=Wink, M|journal=Zeitschrift for Naturforschung C|year=1995|volume=50|issue=11/12|pages=868–82|url=http://www.uni-heidelberg.de/institute/fak14/ipmb/phazb/pdf-files/1995%20Pdf.Pubwink/24.%201995.pdf|access-date=2010-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120316083636/http://www.uni-heidelberg.de/institute/fak14/ipmb/phazb/pdf-files/1995%20Pdf.Pubwink/24.%201995.pdf|archive-date=2012-03-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=Wink, Michael; Petra Heidrich, Claus Fentzloff|title=A mtDNA phylogeny of sea eagles (genus ''Haliaeetus'') based on nucleotide sequences of the cytochrome b-gene|journal=Biochemical Systematics and Ecology|volume=24|issue=7-8|year=1996|pages=783–91|doi=10.1016/S0305-1978(96)00049-X}}</ref>有些學者更建議將它們分類到新的[[胡兀鷲亞科|胡兀鷲亞科]]之中。<ref>{{cite journal|first1=Ingrid|last1=Seibold|first2=Andreas J.|last2=Helbig|title=Evolutionary History of New and Old World Vultures Inferred from Nucleotide Sequences of the Mitochondrial Cytochrome b Gene|journal=Phil. Trans. R. Soc. Lond. B|year=1995|volume=350|issue=1332|pmid=8577858|pages=163–78|doi=10.1098/rstb.1995.0150}}</ref>現時廣泛接受的有三個白兀鷲的亞種，但它們之間卻有很多[[混種|混種]]。<ref name=Donazar2002>{{cite journal|author=Donázar, José Antonio; Negro, Juan José; Palacios, César Javier; Gangoso, Laura; Godoy, José Antonio; Ceballos, Olga; Hiraldo, Fernando; & Capote, Nieves|year=2002|title=Description of a new subspecies of the Egyptian Vulture (Accipitridae: ''Neophron percnopterus'') from the Canary Islands|journal=Journal of Raptor Research|volume=36|issue=1|pages=17–23|url=http://www.cesarjpalacios.com/Subespecie%20JRR.pdf|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708132903/http://www.cesarjpalacios.com/Subespecie%20JRR.pdf|archivedate=2011-07-08}}</ref>[[俾路支地區|俾路支地區]]及[[喜瑪拉雅山|喜瑪拉雅山]]西北部的''N. p. rubripersonatus''並未獲得確認。<ref name=pcr/><ref>{{cite book|url=http://www.archive.org/stream/dievgelderpal02hart#page/1200/mode/1up|pages=1200–2|title=Die Vögel der paläarktischen Fauna. Volume 2|first=Ernst|last=Hartert|publisher=Friendlander & Sohn, Berlin|year=1910}}</ref>
* ''N. p. percnopterus''：指名亞種，其分佈最廣，包括[[南歐|南歐]]、[[北非|北非]]、[[中東|中東]]、[[中亞|中亞]]及[[印度次大陸|印度次大陸]]。它們在[[溫帶|溫帶]]地區[[繁殖|繁殖]]，並會向南過冬。
* ''N. p. ginginianus''：體型最細小的亞種，喙呈淡色。它們分佈在印度次大陸的大部份地區。其名是衍生自[[印度|印度]]南部的[[京吉|京吉]]（Gingee）。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Buceros |volume=9 |issue=2 |year=2004 |title=A dictionary of scientific bird names originating from the Indian region |author=Pittie A |url=http://www.bnhsenvis.nic.in/pdf/Vol%209%20(2)dictionary.pdf |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100401022658/http://www.bnhsenvis.nic.in/pdf/Vol%209%20%282%29dictionary.pdf |archivedate=2010-04-01 }}</ref>
* ''N. p. majorensis''：體型最大的亞種。它們分佈在[[加那利群島|加那利群島]]，群落數量最少及最受限制。於2002年才確立為一個亞種，它們的[[基因|基因]]較為接近''N. p. percnopterus''，而疏於''N. p. ginginianus''。它們不是[[候鳥|候鳥]]。其名字是衍生自[[富埃特文圖拉島|富埃特文圖拉島]]的古代名字。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Conservation Genetics|title=Genetically distinct island populations of the Egyptian vulture (''Neophron percnopterus'')|volume=4|issue=6|pages=697–706|year=2003|author=Kretzmann MB; N. Capote; B. Gautschi; J.A. Godoy; J.A. Donázar & J.J. Negro|doi=10.1023/B:COGE.0000006123.67128.86|url=http://www.ebd.csic.es/carnivoros/personal/donazar/joseadonazar/s_p_pdfs/108_Genetically%20distinct%20island%20populations%20of%20the%20Egyptian%20vulture_Kretzmann.pdf|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720140943/http://www.ebd.csic.es/carnivoros/personal/donazar/joseadonazar/s_p_pdfs/108_Genetically%20distinct%20island%20populations%20of%20the%20Egyptian%20vulture_Kretzmann.pdf|archivedate=2011-07-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=Donázar, José Antonio; Negro, Juan José; Palacios, César Javier; Gangoso, Laura; Godoy, José Antonio; Ceballos, Olga; Hiraldo, Fernando; & Capote, Nieves|year=2002|title=Description of a new subspecies of the Egyptian Vulture (Accipitridae: ''Neophron percnopterus'') from the Canary Islands|journal=Journal of Raptor Research|volume=36|issue=1|pages=17–23|url=http://www.cesarjpalacios.com/Subespecie%20JRR.pdf|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708132903/http://www.cesarjpalacios.com/Subespecie%20JRR.pdf|archivedate=2011-07-08}}</ref>

白兀鷲屬的屬名是取自[[希臘神話|希臘神話]]的[[涅俄佛隆|涅俄佛隆]]（Neophron）。涅俄佛隆是Timandra的兒子，而Timandra則是Aegypius的情婦。涅俄佛隆將Aegypius的母親幻化成Timandra，欺騙他與其母同寢。他母親醒來後慾奪走他的[[眼睛|眼睛]]，但[[宙斯|宙斯]]卻將涅俄佛斯及Aegypius變成[[禿鷲|禿鷲]]。<ref>{{cite book|title=The dictionary of classical mythology|url=https://archive.org/details/dictionaryofclas0000grim|author=Grimal, Pierre|year=1996|publisher=Wiley-Blackwell|page=[https://archive.org/details/dictionaryofclas0000grim/page/18 18]|isbn=0631201025}}</ref>[[種小名|種小名]]則是指其黑色的雙翼。<ref name=etym>{{cite journal|last=Koenig, Alexander|first1=Alexander|title=Die Geier Aegyptens|journal=Journal of Ornithology|year=1907|pages=59–134|volume=55|issue=1|doi=10.1007/BF02098853|language=de}}</ref>

== 分佈 ==
白兀鷲廣泛分佈在[[南歐|南歐]]、[[北非|北非]]、[[西亞|西亞]]及[[南亞|南亞]]。它們主要棲息在乾旱平原。它們有時也會流浪到[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]]<ref name=hbk/>、[[歐洲|歐洲]]北部及[[南非|南非]]。<ref>{{cite journal|author= Mundy PJ|title=The Egyptian vulture (''Neophron Percnopterus'') in Southern Africa|journal= Biological Conservation|volume=14|issue=4|year=1978|pages=307–15|doi=10.1016/0006-3207(78)90047-2}}</ref>歐洲群落會向南遷徙3500-5500公里到達[[非洲|非洲]]，有時單日的旅程長達500公里。在[[法國|法國]]曾有一隻白兀鷲出生第三天就已經向南遷徙。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Meyburg|first1=Bernd-U.|last2=Gallardo|first2=Max|last3=Meyburg|first3=Christiane|last4=Dimitrova|first4=Elena|title=Migrations and sojourn in Africa of Egyptian vultures ( ''Neophron percnopterus'') tracked by satellite|journal=Journal of Ornithology|year=2004|pages=273–80|volume=145|issue=4|doi=10.1007/s10336-004-0037-6}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=First description of migration and wintering of adult Egyptian Vultures ''Neophron percnopterus'' tracked by GPS satellite telemetry|author=García-Ripollés, Clara; Pascual López-López; Vicente Urios|journal=Bird Study|volume=57|issue=2|pages=261-5|year=2010|doi=10.1080/00063650903505762}}</ref>[[義大利|義大利]]的群落會橫跨[[馬雷蒂莫|馬雷蒂莫]]（Marettimo）及[[潘泰萊里亞|潘泰萊里亞]]，經[[西西里島|西西里島]]到達[[突尼西亞|突尼西亞]]。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.2478/v10050-008-0062-6|author=Agostini N., Premuda G., Mellone U., Panuccio M., Logozzo D., Bassi E.,Cocchi L.|year=2004|title=Crossing the sea en route to Africa: autumn migration of some Accipitriformes over two Central Mediterranean islands|journal=Ring|volume=26|issue=2|pages=71–8|url=http://www.raptormigration.org/Agostini%20et%20al%202004%20-%20Ring.pdf|access-date=2010-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120326124750/http://www.raptormigration.org/Agostini%20et%20al%202004%20-%20Ring.pdf|archive-date=2012-03-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 行為及生態 ==
[[File:Egyptian_vulture_in_flight.jpg|thumb]]
白兀鷲經常會隨熱流上升。它們吃多種食物，包括[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]的[[糞便|糞便]]（尤其是[[人類|人類]]<ref>{{cite book|author=Whistler, Hugh|year=1949|title=Popular Handbook of Indian Birds|edition=4|publisher=Gurney & Jackson|pages=356–7|url=http://www.archive.org/stream/popularhandbooko033226mbp#page/n406/mode/1up|isbn=1406745766}}</ref>）、[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]、屍體、[[植物|植物]]及細小的獵物。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Prakash, Vibhu; Nanjappa, C|year=1988|title=An instance of active predation by Scavenger Vulture (''Neophron p. ginginianus'') on Checkered Keelback watersnake (''Xenochrophis piscator'') in Keoladeo National Park, Bharatpur, Rajasthan|journal=J. Bombay Nat. Hist. Soc.|volume=85|issue=2|page=419}}</ref>研究顯示它們吃哺乳動物的糞便可以幫助它們攝取[[類胡蘿蔔素|類胡蘿蔔素]]色素，令其面部[[皮膚|皮膚]]呈鮮黃及橙色。<ref name=carotenoid>{{cite journal|title=An unusual source of essential carotenoids|author=Negro, J. J. Negro, J. M. Grande, J. L. Tella, J. Garrido†, D. Hornero†, J. A. Donázar, J. A. Sanchez-Zapata‡, J. R. Benítez, M. Barcell|year=2002|volume=47|journal=Nature|page=807|url=http://web.uam.es/personal_pdi/ciencias/jonate/Ecologia/Tema%2018/Negro_etal,%202002.pdf|access-date=2010-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140320062324/http://web.uam.es/personal_pdi/ciencias/jonate/Ecologia/Tema%2018/Negro_etal,%202002.pdf|archive-date=2014-03-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>它們一般較為寂靜，但若受到騷擾則會發出高音的叫聲。<ref name=pcr/>

白兀鷲是群居的<ref>{{cite book|author=Donázar JA, Ceballos O, Tella JL|year=1996|chapter=Communal roosts of Egyptian vultures (''Neophron percnopterus''): dynamics and implications for the species conservation|editor=Muntaner J, Mayol J|title=Biology and Conservation of Mediterranean Raptors|publisher=Monografía SEO-BirdLife, Madrid|pages=189–201|url=http://www.ebd.csic.es/carnivoros/personal/donazar/joseadonazar/s_p_pdfs/60_Communal%20roosts%20of%20egyptian%20vultures.pdf|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720140633/http://www.ebd.csic.es/carnivoros/personal/donazar/joseadonazar/s_p_pdfs/60_Communal%20roosts%20of%20egyptian%20vultures.pdf|archivedate=2011-07-20}}</ref>，鳥巢會不斷再用。它們很多時都是單獨或成對的行動。它們是[[一夫一妻制|一夫一妻制]]的，夫妻的關係可以維持多於一個[[繁殖|繁殖]]季節。成年雄鷲在雌鷲生蛋前後很多時都會留在其身邊。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Donázar, J. A. , Ceballos, O. and Tella, J. L.|year=1994|title=Copulation behaviour in the Egyptian Vulture ''Neophron percnopterus''|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_bird-study_1994-03_41_1/page/37|journal= Bird Study|volume=41|issue=1|pages=37–41|doi=10.1080/00063659409477195}}</ref>它們會在峭壁、[[建築物|建築物]]及樹上築巢。<ref name=pcr/>''N. p. ginginianus''及''N. p. majorensis''也會在地上築巢。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Biddulph,CH|year=1937|title=Unusual site for the nest of the White Scavenger Vulture ''Neophron percnopterus ginginianus'' (Lath.)|journal= J. Bombay Nat. Hist. Soc.|volume=39|issue=3|pages=635–6}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=Paynter, WP|year=1924|title=Lesser White Scavenger Vulture ''N. ginginianus'' nesting on the ground|journal=J. Bombay Nat. Hist. Soc.|volume=30|issue=1|pages=224–225}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=Gangoso, Laura|year=2005|title=Ground nesting by Egyptian Vultures (''Neophron percnopterus'') in the Canary Islands|journal=Journal of Raptor Research|volume=39|issue=2|pages=186–7|url=http://www.alimochefuerteventura.com/documentos/Ground-nesting-by%20Egyptian-Vultures.pdf|access-date=2010-11-16|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924155457/http://www.alimochefuerteventura.com/documentos/Ground-nesting-by%20Egyptian-Vultures.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[印度|印度]]群落的繁殖季節是於2月至4月。雙親都會孵蛋，孵化期為42天。<ref name=hbk/>3-5天後就會孵化第二隻雛鷲，但時間越長，其生存率就越低。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Growth rates of nestling Egyptian Vultures ''Neophron percnopterus'' in relation to brood size, hatching order and environmental factors|author=Donazar JA & O Ceballos|pages=217–26|journal=Ardea|year=1989|volume=77|issue=2|url=http://www.ebd.csic.es/carnivoros/personal/donazar/joseadonazar/s_p_pdfs/23_Growth%20rates%20of%20nestling%20Egyptian%20vultures%20Neophron%20percnopterus%20in%20relation%20to%20brood%20size_hatching.pdf|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720140735/http://www.ebd.csic.es/carnivoros/personal/donazar/joseadonazar/s_p_pdfs/23_Growth%20rates%20of%20nestling%20Egyptian%20vultures%20Neophron%20percnopterus%20in%20relation%20to%20brood%20size_hatching.pdf|archivedate=2011-07-20}}</ref>在鳥巢緊迫的地方，雛鷲有時會走到其他鳥巢尋找食物。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Donazar, J. A. & Ceballos O|title=Acquisition of food by fledgling Egyptian Vultures ''Neophron percnopterus'' by nest-switching and acceptance by foster adults|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_ibis_1990-10_132_4/page/603|journal=Ibis|volume=132|issue=4|pages=603|year=1990|doi=10.1111/j.1474-919X.1990.tb00284.x}}</ref>[[西班牙|西班牙]]群落的幼鷲會在90-110天大時換羽及離開鳥巢。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Donazar JA & O Ceballos|title=Post-fledging dependence period and development of flight and foraging behaviour in the Egyptian Vulture ''Neophron percnopterus''|pages=387–94|year=1989|journal=Ardea|volume=78|url=http://www.ebd.csic.es/carnivoros/personal/donazar/joseadonazar/s_p_pdfs/31_Post-fledging%20dependece%20period%20and%20development%20of%20flight%20and%20foraging%20behaviour%20in%20the%20Egyptian%20vult.pdf|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720140755/http://www.ebd.csic.es/carnivoros/personal/donazar/joseadonazar/s_p_pdfs/31_Post-fledging%20dependece%20period%20and%20development%20of%20flight%20and%20foraging%20behaviour%20in%20the%20Egyptian%20vult.pdf|archivedate=2011-07-20}}</ref>幼鷲離開鳥巢後會到遠達500公里以外的地方。<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.icarus.es/product_document/url/79/First_documented_case.pdf|journal=Journal of Raptor Research|volume=43|issue=2|pages=142–5|year=2009|doi=10.3356/JRR-08-53.1|title=First Documented Case of Long-Distance Dispersal in the Egyptian Vulture (''Neophron percnopterus'')|author=Elorriagaa J; Iñigo Zuberogoitiab, Iñaki Castilloc, Ainara Azkonac, Sonia Hidalgoc, Lander Astorkiac, Fernando Ruiz-Moneoc, and Agurtzane Iraetac|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100401031303/http://icarus.es/product_document/url/79/First_documented_case.pdf|archivedate=2010-04-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=Ceballos, O & J A Donazar|year=1990|title=Roost-tree characterstics, food habits and seasonal abundance of roosting Egyptian Vultures in northern Spain|journal=J. Raptor. Res.|volume=24|issue=1-2|pages=19–25|url=http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/jrr/v024n01-02/p00019-p00025.pdf|access-date=2010-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100809081819/http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/jrr/v024n01-02/p00019-p00025.pdf|archive-date=2010-08-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>到了4-5歲大時，它們就會擁有成鳥的[[羽毛|羽毛]]。飼養的白兀鷲壽命可達37歲。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Oikos|volume=118|pages=580–90|year=2009|doi=10.1111/j.1600-0706.2009.17218.x|title=Survival in a long-lived territorial migrant: effects of life-history traits and ecological conditions in wintering and breeding areas|author=Juan M. Grande, David Serrano, Giacomo Tavecchia, Martina Carrete, Olga Ceballos, Ricardo Dıaz-Delgado, Jose L. Tella and Jose A. Donazar|url=http://www.ebd.csic.es/carnivoros/personal/donazar/joseadonazar/s_p_pdfs/139_Survival%20in%20a%20long-lived%20territorial%20migrant%20Egyptian%20vulture_Grande%20et%20al%20Oikos%202009.pdf|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720140846/http://www.ebd.csic.es/carnivoros/personal/donazar/joseadonazar/s_p_pdfs/139_Survival%20in%20a%20long-lived%20territorial%20migrant%20Egyptian%20vulture_Grande%20et%20al%20Oikos%202009.pdf|archivedate=2011-07-20}}</ref>

成年白兀鷲並沒有很多天敵，但很多時卻死於電纜、[[污染|污染]]及中毒。幼鷲會被[[金雕|金雕]]、[[雕鴞|雕鴞]]及[[赤狐|赤狐]]掠食。從峭壁上掉下的白兀鷲也會被[[胡狼|胡狼]]所撿走。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Stoyanova, Y. and N. Stefanov.|year=1993|title=Predation upon nestling Egyptian Vultures (''Neophron percnopterus'') in the Vratsa Mountains of Bulgaria|journal=J. Raptor Res.|volume=27|issue=2|page=123|url=http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/jrr/v027n02/p00123-p00123.pdf|access-date=2010-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100809085449/http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/jrr/v027n02/p00123-p00123.pdf|archive-date=2010-08-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

指名亞種是懂得使用工具的。它們會用喙將大卵石擲向大蛋，將其敲碎。<ref>{{Cite journal|doi=10.1038/2121468a0|volume=212|issue=5069|pages=1468–9|last=van Lawick-Goodall|first=Jane|coauthors=Hugo van Lawick|title=Use of Tools by the Egyptian Vulture, ''Neophron percnopterus''|journal=Nature|date=1966-12-24}}</ref>不過在''N. p. ginginianus''中卻看不見這種行為。<ref name=pcr/>研究發現這種行為並非學習得來的，而是天生的。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Thouless CR, Fanshawe JH, Bertram BCR|title=Egyptian Vultures ''Neophron percnopterus'' and Ostrich ''Struthio camelus'' eggs: the origins of stone-throwing behaviour|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_ibis_1989-01_131_1/page/9|journal=Ibis|year=1989|volume=131|issue=1|pages=9–15|doi=10.1111/j.1474-919X.1989.tb02737.x}}</ref>[[保加利亞|保加利亞]]群落也有使用樹枝來捲起羊毛，用以製作鳥巢。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Raptor Research|volume=44|issue=2|pages=154–6|year=2010|doi=10.3356/JRR-09-20.1|title=Twig Used as a Tool by the Egyptian Vulture (''Neophron percnopterus'')|author=Stoyanova, Yva; Nikolai Stefanova and Josef K Schmutz}}</ref>

== 保育狀況 ==
[[File:Neophron_percnopterus_-_01.jpg|right]]。]]
[[File:Neophron_percnopterus_MHNT.ZOO.2010.11.79.1.jpg|thumb]]
白兀鷲在大部份分佈地中都正經歷嚴重的衰落。在[[歐洲|歐洲]]及[[中東|中東]]大部份地區，其數量只有20年前的一半；在[[印度|印度]]及[[非洲|非洲]]西南部，它們的數量也大幅減少。於1967年至1970年，在[[德里|德里]]附近地區就估計只有12000-15000隻白兀鷲，平均[[密度|密度]]為每10平方公里約有5對。<ref>{{cite book|chapter=Populations of vultures and other raptors in Delhi and neighboring areas from 1970's TO 1990's|author=Galushin VM|pages=13–5|title=Report from the Workshop on Indian ''Gyps'' vultures: 4th Eurasian congress on raptors, Sevilla, Spain|year=2001|editor=Parry-Jones J & T Katzner|url=http://www.aviary.org/cons/pdf/Vulture%20Workshop%20Reports_Seville%202001.pdf|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716202444/http://www.aviary.org/cons/pdf/Vulture%20Workshop%20Reports_Seville%202001.pdf|archivedate=2011-07-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=Galushin VM|title=A comparative analysis of the density of predatory birds in two selected areas within the Palaearctic and Oriental regions, near Moscow and Delhi (IOC Abstracts)|page=331|journal=Emu|volume=74|year=1975}}</ref>引起衰落的原因不明，但卻與使用[[非甾體抗炎藥|非甾體抗炎藥]][[雙氯芬酸鈉|雙氯芬酸鈉]]有關。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Cuthbert R, Green R.E, Ranade S, Saravanan S.S, Pain D.J, Prakash V, Cunningham A.A|year=2006|title=Rapid population declines of Egyptian vulture Neophron percnopterus and red-headed vulture Sarcogyps calvus in India|journal=Anim. Conserv.|volume=9|pages=349–54|doi=10.1111/j.1469-1795.2006.00041.x}}</ref>在[[南歐|南歐]]，它們的衰落也與[[鉛中毒|鉛中毒]]、使用[[殺蟲劑|殺蟲劑]]和[[觸電|觸電]]有關。<ref name=canary>{{cite journal|first=Jose A.|last=Donazar|coauthors=Cesar J. Palacios, Laura Gangoso, Olga Ceballos, Maria J. Gonzalez, Fernando Hiraldo|title=Conservation status and limiting factors in the endangered population of Egyptian vulture (''Neophron percnopterus'') in the Canary Islands|journal=Biological Conservation|volume=107|issue=1|year=2002|pages=89–97|doi=10.1016/S0006-3207(02)00049-6|url=http://www.cesarjpalacios.com/Biologicalconservation.pdf|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708132954/http://www.cesarjpalacios.com/Biologicalconservation.pdf|archivedate=2011-07-08}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|journal=European Journal of Wildlife Research|title=Poison-related mortality effects in the endangered Egyptian vulture (''Neophron percnopterus'') population in Spain|volume=55|issue=4|pages=415–23|year=2009|author=Hernández, Mauro & Antoni Margalida|doi=10.1007/s10344-009-0255-6|url=http://www.gypaetus.com/fotos/noticias/Hern_ndez___Margalida_2009.pdf|access-date=2010-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140320062324/http://www.gypaetus.com/fotos/noticias/Hern_ndez___Margalida_2009.pdf|archive-date=2014-03-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[西班牙|西班牙]]的研究發現吸收[[抗生素|抗生素]]會抑制它們的[[免疫系統|免疫系統]]，造成較易的感染。<ref>{{cite journal|journal= Proc. Biol. Sci.|year=2009|volume=276|issue=1665|pmid=19324751|pmc=2677603|pages=2307–13|doi=10.1098/rspb.2009.0071|title=Cellular and humoral immunodepression in vultures feeding upon medicated livestock carrion|author=Lemus, Jesús A. and Guillermo Blanco}}</ref>

[[加那利群島|加那利群島]]群落與歐洲及非洲的群落分隔了一段頗長時間，而且大幅下降。它們以往廣佈在[[戈梅拉島|戈梅拉島]]、[[特內里費島|特內里費島]]、[[大加那利島|大加那利島]]、[[富埃特文圖拉島|富埃特文圖拉島]]及[[蘭薩羅特島|蘭薩羅特島]]，但現已只限於富埃特文圖拉島、蘭薩羅特島和兩個最東的[[島嶼|島嶼]]。它們的數量於2000年估計約有130隻，共25-30繁殖對。<ref name=canary/><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Bird Conservation International|year=2004|volume=14|pages=203–13|doi=10.1017/S0959270904000103|title=Current status and distribution of birds of prey in the Canary Islands|first4=Boris|last4=SchrÖder|first3=Veronika|last3=Schmidt|first2=H. Martin|last2=Schaefer|author=Palacios, Cesar-Javier|url=http://rapacescanarias.galeon.com/Birds.pdf|access-date=2010-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230040/http://rapacescanarias.galeon.com/Birds.pdf|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>這些島嶼群落特別容易受到感染。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Gangoso L, Grande JM, Lemus JA, Blanco G, Grande J & José A. Donázar|year=2009|title=Susceptibility to Infection and Immune Response in Insular and Continental Populations of Egyptian Vulture: Implications for Conservation|journal=PLoS ONE|pmid=19623256|volume=4|issue=7|pmc=2709727|page=e6333|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0006333}}</ref>在吃腐肉的時候，它們積聚了大量的[[鉛|鉛]]，令其[[骨頭|骨頭]]礦物化。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Gangoso L; Pedro Alvarez-Lloret; Alejandro. A.B. Rodriguez-Navarro; Rafael Mateo; Fernando Hiraldo and Jose Antonio Donazar|title= Long-term effects of lead poisoning on bone mineralization in vultures exposed to ammunition source|journal= Environmental Pollution|volume=157|issue=2|year=2009|pmid=18995938|pages=569–74|doi=10.1016/j.envpol.2008.09.015 }}</ref>現時有措施提供安全及沒有污染的食物，不過缺點是會吸引其他掠食性[[動物|動物]]，增加對雛鷲的危害。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Cortés-Avizanda, A., Carrete, M., Serrano, D. and Donázar, J. A.|year=2009|title=Carcasses increase the probability of predation of ground-nesting birds: a caveat regarding the conservation value of vulture restaurants|journal=Animal Conservation|volume=12|pages=85–8|doi=10.1111/j.1469-1795.2008.00231.x}}</ref>

2012年4月2日在新疆喀什乌恰县发现了一只白兀鹫，这是该鸟在中国分布的新记录。<ref>{{cite web |title=新疆鸟友今年发现三个鸟类新记录 六种罕见鸟种 |url=http://xj.sina.com.cn/news/2018-12-10/detail-ihprknvu0768459.shtml |website=新浪新疆 |access-date=2021-09-28 |archive-date=2021-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210928030615/http://xj.sina.com.cn/news/2018-12-10/detail-ihprknvu0768459.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

